1. *Ovakvom* lepotom nisam se dugo divio. (I haven't admired *such* beauty in a long time.)
2. Ne želim da me prijatelji vide u *ovakvom* stanju. (I don't want my friends to see me in *this* state.)
3. *Ovakvom* situacijom sam se već susreo. (I've already encountered *this kind* of situation.)
4. Želim da se vratim *ovakvom* životu. (I want to go back to *this kind of* life.)
5. Da li ti se sviđa *ovakva* hrana? (Do you like *this kind* of food?)
6. Mnogi ljudi se suočavaju sa *ovakvim* problemima. (Many people face *such* problems.)
7. Često razmišljam o *ovakvim* stvarima. (I often think about *such* things.)
8. Koliko često dolaziš u *ovakve* kafiće? (How often do you come to *these kinds* of cafes?)
9. Molim te da ne ponavljaš *ovakve* greške. (Please don't repeat *these kinds* of mistakes.)
10. *Ovakve* stvari mi donose sreću. ( *These kinds* of things bring me happiness.)